  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎲 Roll the Dice. Fire the Gun. Laugh at the Chaos.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Bengbo</strong>, a dice-driven FPS roguelike where every bullet is a gamble, every boss is ridiculous, and every run is as unpredictable as a casino slot pull.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Bengbo?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most roguelikes test your reflexes. Bengbo tests your <strong>luck</strong>, and your ability to laugh when that luck runs out. With <strong>full Swedish voice acting</strong>, <strong>casino-themed arenas</strong>, and weapons powered by dice of every shape and size, Bengbo delivers a uniquely chaotic blend of comedy and challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/871a463e371c100c1aeefcb941addc7a.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/48d359d9683a33fc1f99f146550b9c51.poster.avif?t=1766249798\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/48d359d9683a33fc1f99f146550b9c51.webm?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/48d359d9683a33fc1f99f146550b9c51.mp4?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎲 Dice-Powered Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from d4s, d6s, d12s, and even the legendary d20, each die changes how your weapon behaves. Will your next roll save you, or send you into glorious failure?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤖 Absurd Boss Fights</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face casino-themed monstrosities who play by their own rules. Every encounter feels like a bizarre mix of stand-up comedy and bullet hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/f9a00ff0b0a396c27831ec3fd72d9244.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/b04e6abc830854143efdaa3796f9baff.poster.avif?t=1766249798\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/b04e6abc830854143efdaa3796f9baff.webm?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/b04e6abc830854143efdaa3796f9baff.mp4?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏛️ Arena & Lounge System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle through arenas, then cool off in the lounge where you gamble upgrades, unlock new dice, and prepare for your next doomed run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎤 Fully Voiced in Swedish</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every line is delivered with unapologetic Swedish charm. Subtitles included—so you won’t miss a single joke, even if you don’t speak the language.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 Award-Winning Art Style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Winner of <strong>Best Art</strong> at the Swedish Game Awards and nominated for <strong>Best Narrative</strong> 2023.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/63f085e45453c7ec43b528e4468051e3.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/c1887a12dabc4f5afd1c214cf53c2160.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎲 Roll the Dice. Fire the Gun. Laugh at the Chaos.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Bengbo</strong>, a dice-driven FPS roguelike where every bullet is a gamble, every boss is ridiculous, and every run is as unpredictable as a casino slot pull.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Bengbo?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most roguelikes test your reflexes. Bengbo tests your <strong>luck</strong>, and your ability to laugh when that luck runs out. With <strong>full Swedish voice acting</strong>, <strong>casino-themed arenas</strong>, and weapons powered by dice of every shape and size, Bengbo delivers a uniquely chaotic blend of comedy and challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/871a463e371c100c1aeefcb941addc7a.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/48d359d9683a33fc1f99f146550b9c51.poster.avif?t=1766249798\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/48d359d9683a33fc1f99f146550b9c51.webm?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/48d359d9683a33fc1f99f146550b9c51.mp4?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎲 Dice-Powered Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from d4s, d6s, d12s, and even the legendary d20, each die changes how your weapon behaves. Will your next roll save you, or send you into glorious failure?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤖 Absurd Boss Fights</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face casino-themed monstrosities who play by their own rules. Every encounter feels like a bizarre mix of stand-up comedy and bullet hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/f9a00ff0b0a396c27831ec3fd72d9244.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/b04e6abc830854143efdaa3796f9baff.poster.avif?t=1766249798\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/b04e6abc830854143efdaa3796f9baff.webm?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/b04e6abc830854143efdaa3796f9baff.mp4?t=1766249798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏛️ Arena & Lounge System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle through arenas, then cool off in the lounge where you gamble upgrades, unlock new dice, and prepare for your next doomed run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎤 Fully Voiced in Swedish</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every line is delivered with unapologetic Swedish charm. Subtitles included—so you won’t miss a single joke, even if you don’t speak the language.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 Award-Winning Art Style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Winner of <strong>Best Art</strong> at the Swedish Game Awards and nominated for <strong>Best Narrative</strong> 2023.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/63f085e45453c7ec43b528e4468051e3.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475860/extras/c1887a12dabc4f5afd1c214cf53c2160.avif?t=1766249798\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p>",
